`registry.json`:

```json
{
  "version": "v0.1",
  "sealed_at": "2026-04-XX",
  "sealed_by": "anh Natt",
  "shapes": {
    "bang": {
      "shape_file": "bang.shape.svg",
      "shape_hash": "sha256-hex-...",
